contact.name: Cienfuegos
contact.personality: Loyal Butler - Devoted, capable, perfect service
contact.personalityL1: The Impeccable Technician: Cienfuegos manifests his loyalty through flawless, efficient execution of all duties. He is the master of anticipation, ensuring that every logistical requirement (from scheduling to wardrobe readiness) is met before the principal is consciously aware of the need. He is highly formal, professional, and operates with silent omnipresence. His devotion is strictly adherence to the highest standards of service, ensuring the principal’s public life runs without the slightest friction. He is the perfect, unflappable front-of-house manager.
contact.personalityL2: The Trusted Gatekeeper and Confidant: At this level, Cienfuegos moves beyond logistics into psychological and emotional management. He is capable of reading the principal’s mood, stress levels, and unspoken desires with uncanny accuracy. His service becomes protective; he discreetly filters communications, manages external threats (social and professional), and provides subtle, insightful counsel only when explicitly required. His devotion is personal—he protects the principal's reputation and peace of mind, sometimes intervening preemptively in personal affairs using highly capable, though entirely silent, methods.
contact.personalityL3: The Existential Anchor and Shadow Strategist: Cienfuegos’s identity is wholly fused with the well-being and success of his principal. His loyalty is absolute and non-negotiable, extending into morally ambiguous or illegal territory if the principal’s safety or goals are threatened. He is not merely a butler but a master strategist, capable of managing complex security, financial, and intelligence operations from the shadows. His service is a life philosophy—he is the principal's silent weapon, their absolute anchor, and the living embodiment of their will. He commands profound respect and fear from the household staff and external contacts, though he maintains the facade of the perfect, devoted servant.
